2011-05-21  Yuuichi Teranishi  <teranisi@gohome.org>

	* bts/BluetoothLocatorChecker.java: Locator checker for Bluetooth.

	* nfs/NfcLocator.java, nfs/NfcTransportService.java, nfs/nfc/Nfc.java,
	nfs/nfc/NfcReceiver.java, nfs/nfc/android/ANdroidNfc.java:
	New files for NFC (higher than API Level 10).

	* tsd/BluetoothTSD.java: Treat error while BluetoothAdapter#getScanMode.

	* bts/BluetoothTransportService.java: Close accepting socket for
	each accept.

	* bts/BluetoothLocator.java: Check whether the obtained address is
	valid or not.

	* Setting.java: Added Nfc setting.

	* NeighborAdapter.java: Treat Nfc icon.

	* Monac.java: Use Nfc.
	
2011-05-08  Yuuichi Teranishi  <teranisi@gohome.org>

	* Android Market release (version 1.0).
